Description: Segmented-Spacetime Suite (extended)
 Complete analysis pipeline for segmented spacetime cosmology.
 Includes:
  - Ring temperature → velocity predictions
  - EHT shadow comparison (χ² tests)
  - Redshift robustness analysis (Bootstrap/Jackknife)
  - Full test suite with automated reports
  - Anti-Capitalist Software License (v 1.4)
 .
 Runs the full pipeline, prints all reports and license at the end.
 Optional data autofetch to avoid bundling multi-GB datasets.
